##### 29 try中return A，catch中return B，finally中return C，最终返回值是什么？

```java
public class Example {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println(testMethod());
    }

    public static String testMethod() {
        try {
            //System.out.print(1/0); 异常代码
            return "A";
        } catch (Exception e) {
